<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Justin Bieber and Hailey Baldwin commemorated their two-year wedding anniversary with with a delicious picnic on Saturday. </p>

<p>The couple, who previously shocked the world by tying the knot in a surprise courthouse ceremony in NYC, proved they were still happy in love during a brief trip to their favorite deli. </p>

<p>Before finding a grassy location to enjoy an array of snacks, the 23-year-old model and Grammy winner, 26, were seen waiting in line for sandwiches at Bay Cities Italian Deli &amp; Bakery in Santa Monica.</p>

