<p>The Yummy hitmaker sported a white t-shirt, light blue beanie and a pair of grey shorts, as he chatted on the phone. </p>

<p>Meanwhile, the 5ft 7in beauty showcased her gym-honed midriff in a cropped Alexander Wang top and light-wash denim bottoms. </p>

<p>As they stood at the entrance, the Vogue cover girl kept her arms folded across her chest, while wearing a black CDC-recommended face mask.  </p>

